short_description: The US-JDDT-800 machine of this model, with a production speed of 40 to 160 pieces per minute, has a weight of 3200 kg. The total capacity is 15 kW. The width of the produced bags is 400-650 mm, and the length is 400-680 mm. Equipment size: length 7000 mm, width 2000 mm and height 2200 mm. There are other models in the description. Their prices and parameters differ from each other.
